{
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "tasks": [
    {
      "label": "build",                 // This name must match the one referenced in launch.json
      "type": "shell",
      "command": "g++",
      "args": [
        "-g",                           // For debugging
        "main.cpp",                     // Your source file
        "-o",
        "main"                          // The name of the executable
      ],
      "group": {
        "kind": "build",
        "isDefault": true
      },
      "problemMatcher": ["$gcc"]
    }
  ]
}
Make sure this file is located at:
/.vscode/tasks.json

2. Create or update .vscode/launch.json
This tells the debugger how to launch your program.

json
Copy
